content: There will be two different files in the folder.

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message indicating that two files will be copied. It appears in a conflict resolution dialog and provides context for users when choosing how to proceed with conflicting file names.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Es werden zwei verschiedene Dateien in dem Ordner vorhanden sein' is overly formal and verbose. A more natural translation would be 'Es gibt zwei verschiedene Dateien im Ordner.' or 'In dem Ordner befinden sich zwei verschiedene Dateien.'
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Es gibt zwei verschiedene Dateien im Ordner.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'vorhanden sein' is grammatically correct but sounds unnecessarily formal and clunky in this context. It's better to use a more direct construction.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Removed 'vorhanden sein' and restructured the sentence

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Korean translation '폴더에 두 개의 다른 파일이 저장됩니다' implies that the files are being saved into the folder. The English sentence only states they exist within the folder, not that they are being saved.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 폴더 안에 두 개의 다른 파일이 있습니다.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Lao translation "ໃນໂຟນເດີ້ຈະມີ 2 ໄຟລ໌ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ." while conveying the general meaning, is slightly awkward. A more natural translation would emphasize the distinct nature of the files.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ໃນໂຟນເດີ້ຈະມີໄຟລ໌ສອງຢ່າງທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Romanian translation 'Două fișiere diferite vor fi salvate în dosarul' implies that the files *will be saved* in the folder. The English sentence simply states their existence *in* the folder. The Romanian translation adds an action that isn't present in the original.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Două fișiere diferite vor fi în dosar.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'බහාලුමෙහි වෙනස් ගොනු දෙකක් ඇත' while conveying the general meaning, is not the most natural or accurate translation of 'There will be two different files in the folder.' A more appropriate translation would use a word for 'folder' that is more commonly used in this context. 'බහාලුම' can mean a basket or container, but a more direct equivalent of 'folder' would enhance clarity.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: There are several options. Consider 'සමූහයෙහි වෙනස් ගොනු දෙකක් ඇත' (samūhayehi venaś gōnu dekak athā) where 'සමූහය' (samūhaya) translates closer to 'group' or 'collection' which is a better equivalent for 'folder' in this context. Alternatively, 'ලේඛන සාමග්‍රහියේ වෙනස් ගොනු දෙකක් ඇත' (lēkhana sāmāgrahīye venaś gōnu dekak athā) is also possible with 'ලේඛන සාමග්‍රහිය' meaning 'document repository' which can be used for a folder.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'folder' is transliterated as 'фолдеру'. While understandable, using the Serbian equivalent 'фасцикула' would be more natural and culturally appropriate.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Биће две различите датотеке у фасцикула.
